===Etymology===
STEDT compares it to {{cog|tbq-pro|*m/s-prat ~ *pran||to sprinke; to spray}}, whence {{cog|my|ဖျန်း||to spray, to sprinkle}}. On the other hand, {{zh-ref|Schuessler (2007)}} compares it to {{cog|lus|phuh||to blow out of the mouth}}, {{cog|bo|ཕུ་བ||to blow}}. 

